title: ArtyTorrent Pack 32-Funky Acoustic Drum Loops 110-129bpm-WAV sam
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 32-Funky Acoustic Drum Loops 110-129bpm-WAV samples
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Hi there samplists!
This pack was inspired by a couple of requests for some "live" drum sounds.
Included are drumloops on a funky tip with the majority being recordings of acoustic drumkits played "live", and without any digital signal processing effects.

Torrent contains 2 RAR files.
Arty&#039;s Funky Breaks 110-119 vol.1 (52 drumloops)
and
Arty&#039;s Funky Breaks 120-129 vol.1 (97 drumloops)

All samples are normalized 16-bit Acidized WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the bpm in the filename, ready to be dropped into your own productions, or chopped up and effected as you wish.

The samples are from a variety of sources too numerous to list here.

I categorize all my samples by tempo and style, so you can expect
future packs of drumloops along the lines of "digital breaks 130-139", "electro 115", "four to the floor 125", "hard techno 140", "drum n&#039; bass 160+" etc.

I hope you find this pack useful and inspiring.

--
Arty - "Keep on doing what you&#039;re doing, but make it funky!"
1st February 2008.
